### 1. 쿠폰 생성 (Admin)
POST http://localhost:8080/coupons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "couponName": "오프라인 이벤트 쿠폰",
  "discountType": "FIXED",
  "discountValue": 5000,
  "minOrderAmount": 10000,
  "maxDiscountAmount": 5000,
  "startDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00",
  "endDate": "2024-12-31T23:59:59",
  "usageLimit": 100,
  "issueCount": 0
}

> {%
    client.global.set("couponId", response.body.id);
%}

### 2. 오프라인 쿠폰 대량 발급
POST http://localhost:8080/coupons/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "couponId": {{couponId}},
  "count": 5
}

> {%
    client.global.set("couponCode", response.body[0].code);
%}

### 3. 사용자 쿠폰 등록 (Offline Claim)
POST http://localhost:8080/coupons/Issuance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "couponCode": "{{couponCode}}",
  "userId": 1
}

### 4. 사용자 쿠폰 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/coupons/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. 이미 사용된 쿠폰 재등록 시도 (실패해야 함 - 409 Conflict)
POST http://localhost:8080/coupons/Issuance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "couponCode": "{{couponCode}}",
  "userId": 2
}
